", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "LLVM has the `llvm.assume` intrinsic, represented by `__builtin_assume` in clang. Since GCC does not have this intrinsic, we need to lower `core::intrinsics::assume(<condition>)` to the following pseudo code:\r\n\r\n```c\r\nif (!<condition>)\r\n    __builtin_unreachable();\r\n```\r\n\r\nor\r\n```c\r\n__builtin_expect(<condition>, <true>);\r\n```\r\n\r\nwhich should hopefully enable us to gain some optimizations", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/issues/1561/reactions", "total_count": 1, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 1}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/issues/1561/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}